dct_title_s: Spain 1:10,000. Salamanca city plan. A.M.S. M981
dct_description_sm: Map shows military and coast guard headquarters. Some streets and buildings are named. Oriented with north toward the upper right. " Copied from Spanish map 1:9,600, Patronato Nacional Del Turismo, Salamanca. Grid and projection approximate." "Army Map Service, U. S. Army, Washington, D. C. 114804. 1943. 3-43." Military grid. Alternate title: Salamanca city plan. Copied from Spanish map, 1:9,600, Patronato Nacional del Turismo, Salamanca. Projection approximate. AMS 1.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1943.
